 Plane of Valor and Halls of Honor access<br>
<br>
Okay, I see a lot of speculation going on here and I see a lot of questions regarding flags and quests to get you into these zones. As a particular interest to Paladins the planes of honor seems especially important for us. So, I did a little research and I'm posting information here for you all to use.<br>
