Okay, first is the Flagging for Plane of Valor. This can be obtained through a trial in the Plane of Justice. Get a good group together head to the basement and find the quest giver; Mavuin. You will most likely have to kill a few mobs to get to him.<br>
<br>
Trial of Lashing<br>
<br>
